    ‚àá spec‚Üê_BuildOpenAPI;paths;r;pathKey;pathNS;method;op;opts;segs;varMask;param;pNS;ct;code;schemaNS;e;respNS;respKey;ctKey
      :Access Private Instance
      ‚çù _Mangle mangles strings into valid APL names; ‚éïJSON will unmangle them
      spec‚Üê(
        openapi: '3.0.3'
        info: Info
      )
      ctKey‚Üê_Mangle'application/json'

      paths‚Üê()
      :For r :In _routes
          :If '_'=‚äÉr.handler ‚ãÑ :Continue ‚ãÑ :EndIf   ‚çù skip internal routes

          ‚çù Get or create path object
          pathKey‚Üê_Mangle r.pattern
          :If 0=paths.‚éïNC‚äÇpathKey
              paths ‚éïVSET ‚äÇpathKey ()
          :EndIf
          pathNS‚Üêpaths ‚éïVGET pathKey

          ‚çù Build operation object
          method‚Üê‚éïC r.method
          op‚Üê(
            parameters: ‚ç¨
            responses: ()
          )

          ‚çù Map metadata from route options
          opts‚Üêr.options
          op.operationId‚Üêr.handler

          ‚çù Extract path parameters from {param} segments
          ‚çù If opts.params.{name} exists, its schema overrides the default 'string'
          segs‚Üê'/'(‚âÝ‚äÜ‚ä¢)r.pattern
          varMask‚Üê'{'=‚äÉ¬®segs
          :For param :In {1‚Üì¬Ø1‚Üì‚çµ}¬®varMask/segs
              :If 9=‚éïNC'opts' ‚ãÑ :AndIf 9=opts.‚éïNC'params' ‚ãÑ :AndIf 9=opts.params.‚éïNC‚äÇparam
                  pNS‚Üê(name: param ‚ãÑ in: 'path' ‚ãÑ required: (‚äÇ'true') ‚ãÑ schema: (opts.params‚çéparam))
              :Else
                  pNS‚Üê(name: param ‚ãÑ in: 'path' ‚ãÑ required: (‚äÇ'true') ‚ãÑ schema: (type: 'string'))
              :EndIf
              op.parameters,‚Üê‚äÇpNS
          :EndFor
          :If 9=‚éïNC'opts'
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'operationId'  ‚ãÑ op.operationId‚Üêopts.operationId  ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'summary'      ‚ãÑ op.summary‚Üêopts.summary          ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'description'  ‚ãÑ op.description‚Üêopts.description  ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2‚â§opts.‚éïNC'parameters'   ‚ãÑ op.parameters,‚Üêopts.parameters   ‚ãÑ :EndIf
              :If 2=opts.‚éïNC'tags'
                :If 2=‚â°opts.tags
                  op.tags‚Üêopts.tags
                :Else
                  ‚éïSIGNAL ‚äÇ'tags must be a vector of character vectors. Depth 2'
                :EndIf
              :EndIf
              

              ‚çù Request body schema
              :If 9=opts.‚éïNC'body'
                  ct‚Üê() ‚éïVSET ‚äÇctKey (schema: opts.body)
                  op.requestBody‚Üê(required: (‚äÇ'true') ‚ãÑ content: ct)
              :EndIf

              ‚çù Success response: (statusCode schema)
              :If 2‚â§opts.‚éïNC'response'
                  (code schemaNS)‚Üêopts.response
                  ct‚Üê() ‚éïVSET ‚äÇctKey (schema: schemaNS)
                  respNS‚Üê(description: 'Successful response' ‚ãÑ content: ct)
                  respKey‚Üê_Mangle‚çïcode
                  op.responses ‚éïVSET ‚äÇrespKey respNS
              :EndIf

              ‚çù Error responses: vector of (statusCode description) pairs
              :If 2‚â§opts.‚éïNC'errors'
                  :For e :In opts.errors
                      respKey‚Üê_Mangle‚çï‚äÉe
                      op.responses ‚éïVSET ‚äÇrespKey (description: 2‚äÉe)
                  :EndFor
              :EndIf
          :EndIf
          :If 0=‚â¢op.parameters ‚ãÑ op.‚éïEX'parameters' ‚ãÑ :EndIf

          ‚çù Default 200 response if none specified
          :If 0=‚â¢op.responses.‚éïNL ¬Ø2 ¬Ø9
              respKey‚Üê_Mangle'200'
              op.responses ‚éïVSET ‚äÇrespKey (description: 'Successful response')
          :EndIf

          pathNS ‚éïVSET ‚äÇmethod op
      :EndFor

      spec.paths‚Üêpaths
