    ‚àá Start port;code;j
      :Access Public Instance
      code‚Üê‚éïNS ''
      code.inst‚Üê‚éïTHIS
      code.Get‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Post‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Put‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Delete‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      code.Patch‚Üê{inst._Dispatch ‚çµ}
      j‚Üê‚éïNEW (‚äÉ‚äÉ‚éïCLASS ‚éïTHIS).##.Jarvis
      j.Port‚Üêport
      j.Paradigm‚Üê'REST'
      j.CodeLocation‚Üêcode
      j.RESTFailProcessing‚Üê1
      j.Debug‚Üê+/(1 4 8 16)√ó1=2|‚åäDebug√∑1 4 8 16   ‚çù forward bits 1,4,8,16; bit 2 is replaced by Stark's bit 64/2
      :If ''‚â¢ThreadMode
          j.DYALOG_JARVIS_THREAD‚ÜêThreadMode
      :EndIf
      j.Start
      _jarvis‚Üêj
